  %% Diagram 55: Short-Form Video Feed Ranking and Commerce Actions Flow

  Open[Buyer opens reels feed]
  Rank[Rank candidates using\ninterest + trend + affinity + recency]
  Sparse{Sparse user history?}
  Fallback[Use popularity + recency fallback ranking]
  Feed[Render ranked feed cards]

  View[View/impression event]
  Click[Tagged product click]
  Cart[Add to cart]
  Profile[Open vendor profile]

  Open --> Rank --> Sparse
  Sparse -- Yes --> Fallback --> Feed
  Sparse -- No --> Feed

  Feed --> View
  Feed --> Click --> Cart
  Feed --> Profile
